Task: Change file owner/group and observe access effects.

Example:
$ touch file.txt
$ ls -la
-rw-r--r-- 1 macbookpro staff 0 Jan 28 12:00 file.txt

# Change owner and group:
$ sudo chown lab6user:lab6group file.txt
$ ls -la
-rw-r--r-- 1 lab6user lab6group 0 Jan 28 12:00 file.txt

# Test access as another user:
$ sudo -u lab6user cat file.txt
$ sudo -u lab6user echo "hi" >> file.txt
# If permission denied, adjust:
$ sudo chmod 640 file.txt
$ sudo -u lab6user cat file.txt
